# PixEagle external binary manifest.
#
# This file is the source of truth for setup-time MAVSDK Server and
# MAVLink2REST downloads. Keep values as simple KEY=VALUE pairs so both POSIX
# shell and Windows batch setup scripts can read the same manifest.
#
# Update rules:
# - Pin exact upstream release tags.
# - Pin exact asset filenames for each supported platform.
# - Pin SHA-256 digests from the upstream GitHub release asset metadata.
# - Do not use floating "latest" URLs in default setup paths.

